text: Arena is a village in Iowa County, Wisconsin, USA. There were 844 people living in the village of Arena as of the 2020 census. The village of Arena can be found inside of the town of Arena. The village has an area of 1.2 square miles, says the United States Census Bureau. ==References== ==Other websites== *Information about the Village of Arena, Wisconsin Category:Villages in Wisconsin Category:Iowa County, Wisconsin
title: Arena, Wisconsin
